title: James Band Its been done [TFC]
description:
James Band - Rocks on so many levels

James Band mates their influences from rock, jazz, classical music and metal with their undying love for the 70's classic rock band tradition. Their capricious and spontaneous approach to music finished with a touch of Norwegian ethnicity rekindles the spirit of the golden age of rock in the new millennium. Get ready to experience Norway's best kept secret!
